notes.noteText: NRH spawns our NetworkRunner Prefab which spawns our NetworkPlayer Prefab

KNOWN ISSUES:   Sometimes the NetworkPlayer.cs script won't attach to this and it won't tell you why.  Happened already.  Just delete the script from here, remove the Network Object, I had to copy the code from the NetworkPlayer.cs script and delete it, then remake it, paste it back and then reattach it.   Absolute fart on, but it works again now!
USAGE:   This script controls the NetworkCharacterControllerPrototypeCustom.cs script
